
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
If I were paint, you&#8217;d be a canvas<br />
If I were rain, you&#8217;d be watercolours<br />
If I were salt, you&#8217;d be white sand<br />
If I were the sea, you&#8217;d be high tide</p>
<p>If I were the sky, you&#8217;d be a cloud in it<br />
If I were a star, you&#8217;d be enchanted<br />
If I were night, you&#8217;d be its light<br />
If I were day, you&#8217;d be the moonlight</p>
<p>I&#8217;m the voice from the heart<br />
I&#8217;m a letter addressed to the world<br />
I&#8217;m a mirror of emotion<br />
Of your deep look</p>
<p>I&#8217;m complete in an instant<br />
I give my body in a loving style<br />
I&#8217;m the time that doesn&#8217;t pass<br />
When loneliness embraces me</p>
<p>Kiss the sea, the wind and the moon<br />
I&#8217;m a sun in naked snow<br />
In all the streets of love<br />
You&#8217;ll be mine and I&#8217;ll be yours</p>
<p>Kiss the sea, the wind and the moon<br />
I&#8217;m a sun in naked snow<br />
In all the streets of love<br />
You&#8217;ll be mine and I&#8217;ll be yours</p>
